{"tid":2155248,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Trump：香港市場將會「玩完」，將來沒有人會在香港做生意","createTime":"2020-08-13T15:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T19:22:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1927e7514e250ebdff2d28d39d0061fc53673742","tid":2155248,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普說，在中國的嚴厲管治下，香港的金融中心將「玩完」，永遠不會成功。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普接受霍士財經頻道訪問，特朗普聲稱過去美國在香港以優惠形式投入了大量資金，讓香港發展，現時美國已收回一切，美國取消給予香港特殊貿易地位。<br />\n<br />\n他在訪問中說，香港失去特殊地位，意味着香港將會失去好像紐約和倫敦般吸引企業、並成為全球主要金融中心之一的能力；又說香港在中國的管治下，香港數以千計的人才被抵制，香港永遠不會成功，香港市場將會「玩完」，將來沒有人會在香港做生意。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普重申，新型冠狀病毒疫情爆發後對中國的看法有變，形容從來沒有人好像自己對中國和俄羅斯如此強硬。他強調TikTok不能夠在美國營運，就好像中國電訊設備商華為，原因是它收集到的情報資料會送往中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401659&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR%2FcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=5a4c7015\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401659&h=52c0d81f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=401659</a>"},{"pid":"9e40ba6c0a1353814819ad9b13c7f912874ba996","tid":2155248,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a801d81b5faa2703eea3bcb7711a9177022b10fc","tid":2155248,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"到時香港人照翻工，唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor